node.accessibility_caption: Photo by MAYA THE SAMOYED on June 05, 2021. May be an image of dog, flower, stone-fruit tree and outdoors.

node.text: Hi friends! It has been a while since we last posted. First of all we want to thank everyone for your kind messages and are really sorry for making you worry 🥺💕 To answer the most asked question: Maya is happy and doing great as always! The reason for our inactivity is that I struggled with my mental health and therefore decided to take a break from social media. I used the time to focus on myself and work on building a better mindset. Maya and I had a wonderful time together with family and doggo friends, but we missed you all a lot and are glad to be back 🤗 We appreciate your ongoing support and look forward to sharing Maya's adventures with you again! ✨
